[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    254[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;235;203;139mNo conflicts on clinical accuracy.[38;2;235;203;139m**[38;2;192;197;206m The RA biologic scenario, DAS28 scoring, methotrexate step therapy durations, QuantiFERON-TB screening, and ACR guideline references are all domain-correct. The recipe's framing of prior auth fraud risk (false claims about trial durations) is legally accurate and appropriately serious.[K
