[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    262[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;192;197;206mThe recipe's clinical accuracy is sound, the grounded-generation pattern is the correct architectural choice, and the "Honest Take" delivers genuine production wisdom. The three HIGH findings (IAM scoping, cost estimate accuracy, VPC endpoint completeness) are production-readiness gaps, not design flaws. They are the same category of gap that has appeared across Chapter 2 reviews and should be addressed as a pattern. The MEDIUM findings are real but not deal-breakers, and the LOW findings are polish items before publication.[K
